# SmartML - No-Code AI Platform for Data Science

## Overview
SmartML is a powerful no-code platform that enables users to perform data analysis, build machine learning models, and generate sales predictions without writing a single line of code.

## Features
- 🔐 Authentication (Login/Register)
- 📊 Upload CSV/Excel datasets
- ✅ Automatic data validation and preprocessing
- 📈 Interactive visualizations
- 🤖 AI-powered sales predictions (FCFA)
- 🧠 Model training (Linear Regression, Random Forest)
- 📤 Export results (CSV, Excel, PDF)

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: Next.js 14, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Recharts
- **Backend**: FastAPI, Python 3.12
- **Database**: MySQL
- **ML**: Scikit-learn, Pandas, NumPy

## Installation

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.10+
- Node.js 18+
- MySQL (WampServer recommended)

### Backend Setup
```bash
cd backend
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env  # Configure your database
python app/main.py